<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="97" type="etymology">
<paragraph pageId="10" pageNumber="97">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="10" pageNumber="97">
A combination of the Latin words: 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“niger”">&quot;niger&quot;</normalizedToken>
+ 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“costa”">&quot;costa&quot;</normalizedToken>
, referring to the black pleura.
</paragraph>
